107
00:05:48,726 --> 00:05:52,906
If we scale that level down
to an iPhone with, say,


108
00:05:52,906 --> 00:05:55,956
a 320 point height, he
actually is a bit smaller,


109
00:05:56,126 --> 00:05:57,116
he'll be 50 points high.


